                    <p>All lawyers are thoroughly vetted with verified credentials and professional backgrounds.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    </div>
