                    <p>Browse lawyer profiles and contact information anytime, anywhere with our accessible platform.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                    </div>
